<li>Stedman, T. L. (2000, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="01-15"><a href="/wiki/January_15" title="January 15">January 15</a></span>). <i>Stedman's Medical Dictionary</i> (27th ed.). Philadelphia, PA: <a href="/wiki/Lippincott_Williams_%26_Wilkins" title="Lippincott Williams &amp; Wilkins">Lippincott Williams &amp; Wilkins</a>.</li>
